                <note rend="inline" type="source">835.73/154: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Ambassador in Argentina</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Riddle</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1922-08-07T16:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 7, 1922—4 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>34. Your 50, August 4, noon.<note n="65" xml:id="d278fn65">Not printed.</note>
                </p>
                <p>Please make frequent inquiries of Argentine Government, impressing on authorities
                    extreme urgency and importance [of] matter. Keep Department promptly
                    informed.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Harrison</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
